{
  "stem": "26585.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This Sunday, that young man's name was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came and the tears were rolling down his face.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said-- he didn't-- he only speak-- uh, spoke Serbian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a Serb.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was not a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, they're taking the Jewish people from their homes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I've seen the so-and-so family and the so-and-so with suitcases and they're marching them to the station.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother said, Katy, take your father to the gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- the-- there was no time to-- I said, come.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to go through our yard, then climb a fence, go through yards, sometimes crawl on the ground, then we had to go through an open field on our belly until we saw, way back there, those colorful wagons, the gypsies.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, one little gypsy boy saw us crawling and he must have, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we got there and I explained, we explained, and they said, we'll make a gypsy out of him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said, let us know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father said [INAUDIBLE]-- that was his pet name for me-- the minute it's safe, you come.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said maybe days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We-- we-- we did not come for him right away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We waited several days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was the cattle train that would-- oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I came back, I heard these loud voices.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went in the living room, and there stood three, you know, these tall, six feet some, Gestapo-- in uniform, of course-- with my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother looked at me and said, do you know where your father went?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, he took his Sunday morning walk early this morning, like he always did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hasn't he come back yet?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sorry, gentlemen.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
